    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>To provide insight into the long-term immune response following bivalent vaccines, we sampled vaccinated patients simultaneously co-infected with Delta and BA.1. We reported that simultaneous exposure to the Delta and BA.1 S protein does not confer an additional immune advantage compared to exposure to the Omicron BA.1 S protein alone.</jats:p>",
